import os
from selenium import webdriver
import pickle

driver = webdriver.Chrome()
driver.get('https://www.youtube.com/')
driver.find_element_by_id('search').send_keys('funny cats')
driver.find_element_by_id('search-icon-legacy').click()
driver.implicitly_wait(10)

for link in driver.find_elements_by_css_selector('a#video-title'):
    video_url = link.get_attribute('href')
    driver.get(video_url)
    title = driver.find_element_by_css_selector('h1.title').text
    description = driver.find_element_by_css_selector('div.description').text
    print(f'Title: {title}')
    print(f'Description: {description}')
    cookies = driver.get_cookies()

    os.chmod('/tmp/cookies.pkl', 0o777)

    with open('/tmp/cookies.pkl', 'wb') as f:
        pickle.dump(cookies, f)

    driver.back()

driver.quit()
print('Done!')  # notification of task completion

driver = webdriver.Chrome()
url = 'google.com'
driver.get(url)
with open('/tmp/cookies.pkl', 'rb') as f:
    cookies = pickle.load(f)
for cookie in cookies:
    driver.add_cookie(cookie)
driver.quit()
